<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<h2 id="head-ca40063d0fbd4c2bf7e876c99eae2394fda594ae">The Silver Bolt 'Stone-biter' (6d5) (+20,+15)</h2>
<em>Wherever it strikes, this silver-tipped bolt eats through rock and metal as easily as through flesh. The dwarf-smith who crafted Stone-biter also inscribed the shaft with powerful doom-spells against the orcs and trolls who had destroyed his ancestral home.</em> <p>
It increases your searching, infravision, ability to tunnel and luck by 3. It does extra damage from acid. It is especially deadly against orcs. It is especially deadly against trolls. It allows you to sense the presence of orcs and trolls. 
</p>
